                                    "text": "The **best lender depends on your situation**: for *home-only\/chattel* financing, **JCF Lending Group** is the clearest specialist; for broader manufactured-home options in Florida, **Atlantic Mortgage (FloridaHomeLoans.org)** and **Capital Home Mortgage Florida** both present themselves as dedicated Florida manufactured-home lenders.[8][2][4]\n\nA practical way to choose is:\n\n- **If you are buying only the home, not the land:** **JCF Lending Group** is the strongest fit because it explicitly specializes in *chattel mortgages* and home-only manufactured-home loans in Florida.[8]\n- **If you need FHA, VA, USDA, conventional, or land-plus-home financing:** **Atlantic Mortgage \/ FloridaHomeLoans.org** stands out because it says manufactured-home financing is its primary specialty and lists multiple loan programs, including single-wide eligibility.[2]\n- **If you want a Florida lender emphasizing competitive rates and guidance across manufactured-home programs:** **Capital Home Mortgage Florida** is a reasonable candidate, since it says it specializes in Florida manufactured-home loans and offers both traditional and chattel financing.[4][5]\n\nIf your goal is the *single best overall fit*, **Atlantic Mortgage** is the most versatile specialist from the results because it appears to cover the widest range of manufactured-home loan types in Florida while still claiming manufactured-home focus.[2]\n\nIf you want, I can also compare these lenders by **loan type, down payment, credit flexibility, and whether they finance land + home or home-only**.",
